page.title: 20ST.AMBROSE R.C. SCHOOL
page.content: Children from the the fourth year class aged 10 and 11 have contributed to this survey under the guidance of Mr.Norris.Individual pages have been written by Samantha Taylor,Charlotte Baker,Kerry Kelly,Pina Mazzone,Deasun Walsh,Anna Marie Davies,David Allen, Emma Jolley, Damian Cooper,Allanah Steadman,Gerard Pee,Christian Maguire, Paul Szymamski,Kate Hutton and Clare Nash. Founded in 1885, St.Ambrose has a roll of 180+ pupils and eight teachers providing education for the Roman Catholic population of Kidderminster and district.
